AIRCRAFT ENGINES FROM 1997 UNTIL 2000. MR. MCNERNEY IS ON THE BOARD OF THE FOLLOWING PUBLIC COMPANY IN ADDITION TO THE BOEING COMPANY: THE PROCTER & GAMBLE COMPANY. HE IS ALSO A MEMBER OF VARIOUS BUSINESS AND EDUCATIONAL

ORGANIZATIONS.

RICHARD D. STEPHENS

56

SENIOR VICE PRESIDENT HUMAN RESOURCES AND ADMINISTRATION SINCE SEPTEMBER 2005. HE PREVIOUSLY SERVED AS SENIOR VICE PRESIDENT OF INTERNAL SERVICES AND PRIOR THERETO, HE WAS PRESIDENT OF SHARED SERVICES

GROUP. PRIOR THERETO, HE WAS VICE PRESIDENT AND GENERAL MANAGER, INTEGRATED DEFENSE SYSTEMS HOMELAND SECURITY AND SERVICES, FROM JULY 2002 TO DECEMBER 2003. MR. STEPHENS HAS PREVIOUSLY LED A NUMBER OF BOEING BUSINESSES, INCLUDING SPACE AND

