CONTRACTS (FORMERLY INCLUDED IN N&SS) WERE TRANSFERRED TO THE OTHER SEGMENT. BUSINESS SEGMENT DATA FOR ALL PERIODS PRESENTED HAVE BEEN ADJUSTED TO REFLECT THE REALIGNMENT. SEE NOTE 21.

