BENEFICIARY) CONTINUES TO PARTICIPATE IN PERFORMANCE SHARES AWARDS THAT HAVE BEEN OUTSTANDING FOR AT LEAST ONE YEAR. IN ALL OTHER CASES, PARTICIPANTS FORFEIT UNVESTED AWARDS IF THEIR EMPLOYMENT TERMINATES.

